name: Entology
overview: As of October 30, 2008, Entology, Inc. was acquired by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP. Entology, Inc. operates as a technology-consulting company in the United States. It specializes in architecting, developing, and implementing enterprise technology solutions for companies. The company also provides various services, including business solutions strategy, enterprise architecture, enterprise portals, solutions engineering, document management systems, content management, directory services and security, Web services, and knowledge optimization. Its clients include consumer products, financial services, non-profit, healthcare, insurance, manufacturing, media and entertainment, pharmaceuticals and life sciences, real estate/property, services, technology, telecommunications, transportation, and utilities. Entology, Inc. was founded in 1997 and is based in Bedminster, New Jersey.
